modShortDescription: This mod adds a new recipe for arrows that allows you to make the arrows with scrap polymers instead of feathers.
modDescription:
This mod adds a new recipe for arrows that allows you to make the [arrows](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-ammo/) with scrap polymers instead of feathers.

This is my first mod so yeah.
